SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c04341295
Version: 1

HPSBMU03048 rev.1 - HP Software Executive Scorecard, Remote Execution of
Code, Directory Traversal

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as
soon as possible.

Release Date: 2014-06-17
Last Updated: 2014-06-17

Potential Security Impact: Remote code execution, directory traversal

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
A potential security vulnerability has been identified with HP Executive
Scorecard. The vulnerability could be exploited remotely to allow remote code
execution and directory traversal.

References:
CVE-2014-2609 (ZDI-CAN-2116, SSRT101436)
CVE-2014-2610 (ZDI-CAN-2117, SSRT101435)
CVE-2014-2611 (ZDI-CAN-2120, SSRT101431)

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HP Executive Scorecard v9.40 and v9.41

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2014-2609    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)        10
CVE-2014-2610    (AV:N/AC:H/Au:S/C:C/I:C/A:C)       7.1
CVE-2014-2611    (AV:N/AC:L/Au:S/C:C/I:C/A:C)       9.0
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

The Hewlett-Packard Company thanks Mike Arnold (Bruk0ut) for working with
HP's Zero Day Initiative to report these issues to security-alert@...com.

RESOLUTION

HP has provided updates and guidelines to HP Executive Scorecard v9.40 and
v9.41 to resolve this vulnerability. Please download the patch, install the
patch and then follow the post installation guideline listed below.

HP executive Scorecard version patch
 HP SSO URL

9.41 0001patch
 http://support.openview.hp.com/selfsolve/document/LID/EXSC_00014

9.40 0001patch
 http://support.openview.hp.com/selfsolve/document/LID/EXSC_00013

Follow the below guideline after installation of the recommended patches HP
Executive Scorecard version
 Additional guideline

v9.41 with 9.41 0001patch installed
 http://support.openview.hp.com/selfsolve/document/KM00989446

v9.40 with 9.40 0001patch installed
 http://support.openview.hp.com/selfsolve/document/KM00989446

